OL,3,CThe Guernsey politicians encouraging
OL,4,Cmore women into politics
OL,6,FGuernsey's female politicians have
OL,7,Freleased a campaign video encouraging
OL,8,Fmore women to stand for public office
OL,9,Fin next year's election.
OL,11,FWith an election due in June 2025,
OL,12,FDeputies Tina Bury, Sue Aldwell and
OL,13,FSasha Kazantseva-Miller are urging
OL,14,Fwomen to consider a role in politics.
OL,16,FCurrently, Guernsey has eight female
OL,17,Fdeputies out of the 38 politicians in
OL,18,FGuernsey, with the Women in Public
OL,19,FLife organisation hoping to help women
OL,20,Ftake the first steps towards public
OL,21,Foffice.
