OL,3,CThe Guernsey politicians encouraging
OL,4,Cmore women into politics
OL,6,FDeputy Tina Bury says: "I had been
OL,7,Fspeaking to women about the under-
OL,8,Frepresentation that we have and when
OL,9,Fmy son asked me about it and why I was
OL,10,Fnot standing, I stumbled with my
OL,11,Fanswer.
OL,13,F"I did not want to give him the same
OL,14,Freasons that I had given other people
OL,15,Ffor why I wasn't doing it as I didn't
OL,16,Fthink they were good enough.
OL,18,F"I didn't want him to have the
OL,19,Fimpression that women were not capable
OL,20,Fof these things."
