OL,3,CThe Guernsey politicians encouraging
OL,4,Cmore women into politics
OL,6,FDeputy Sasha Kazantseva-Miller said
OL,7,Fshe was motivated to become a States
OL,8,FMember during the COVID-19 pandemic
OL,9,Fand was elected in the 2020 election.
OL,11,FShe explains: "Probably one of the
OL,12,Fmost important reasons that I did
OL,13,Fdecide to go into politics that year
OL,14,Fwas all the change and transition that
OL,15,Fseemed to be happening.
OL,17,F"As an island experiencing extreme
OL,18,Fdisruption to our lives (and) I
OL,19,Frealised that I wanted to be at the
OL,20,Fdecision-making table."
