OL,3,CThe Guernsey politicians encouraging
OL,4,Cmore women into politics
OL,6,FDeputy Sue Aldwell explains being in
OL,7,Fpublic office provides her with
OL,8,Fopportunities to have her say on core
OL,9,FGuernsey issues.
OL,11,FShe adds: "I have been sat in a
OL,12,Fmeeting with 25 experts on MoneyVal, I
OL,13,Fhave also been sat in other meetings
OL,14,Fabout education and how we are going
OL,15,Fto deal with the primary education
OL,16,Fcurriculum.
OL,18,F"The door is open. Stand."
